room_title: Escape room "The Harry Houdini Trap" by The Fifth Wall Escape Rooms in Detroit
room_description:
Diving into a shadowy world of 1926 Detroit, you and your team must unravel the thrilling puzzles of The Harry Houdini Trap.
Just as Houdini was arriving in Detroit for his fateful last stage performance, a mysterious room was under its final preparations. An unknown person or persons built the room for one purpose: to trap the famed escape artist!
